  "body": "### Description\n\nNow when generating the yaml files for Kubernetes , we need to put the fragments to be added on the final generated file ( target/kubernetes/{deployment-target}.yml) \r\n\r\nThis leads to have duplicated fragments in 3 files.\n\n### Implementation ideas\n\nConsider a 4th file : common.yml that contains fragments that will be added in every target-deployment yaml.\r\n\r\nkubernetes.yml = common.yml + kubernetes.yml + generated files\r\nopenshift.yml = common.yml + openshift.yml + generated files\r\nminikube.yml = common.yml + minikube.yml + generated files",
